Installation:
- upload the archive file into your server
- untar/gunzip the file
# tar xzvf blacklist_mc-vx.y.tgz -C /path/to/playsms/

or go in playsms/web/ and do
# tar xzvf blacklist_mc-vx.y.tgz -C ./

Then create the db go in db/ and do
# mysql -u <login> -p<password> <playsms_db_name> < /path/to/playsms/plugin/tools/blacklist/db/blacklist.sql

Some core function has to be modified.

Note: If you are in version 0.9.5.2 you have to modify checkavailablekeyword() function in fn.php replace true by false and false by true.
